verbose_text: Fourth, genetic disruption of spinal cord GRP-neuron neuropeptide mediated itch establishes that Cysltr2-, Htr1f-, and S1pr1 induced scratch responses require the canonical GRP-spinal cord itch circuit.
evidence: Cysltr2-, Htr1f-, and S1pr1-induced scratch responses require the canonical GRP-spinal cord itch
